t-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">新的一年</span></strong></p><p style="font-size: medium;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">园区基层党建工作将紧紧围绕总体要求</span></strong></p><p style="font-size: medium;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">从以下四个方面深入开展</span></strong></p><p style="font-size: medium;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"><img data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="18" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvn6SGicibbSibcibeTOVuaFMuL0KusUOXgDUlF008spcm1Qh6Fxg1D1u7SsBo7j0OHoBXdDc4AqbMU2oA/?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 18px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: text-bottom;"  /><img data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="18" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvn6SGicibbSibcibeTOVuaFMuL0KusUOXgDUlF008spcm1Qh6Fxg1D1u7SsBo7j0OHoBXdDc4AqbMU2oA/?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 18px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: text-bottom;"  /><img data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="18" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvn6SGicibbSibcibeTOVuaFMuL0KusUOXgDUlF008spcm1Qh6Fxg1D1u7SsBo7j0OHoBXdDc4AqbMU2oA/?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 18px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: text-bottom;"  /><br  /></span></p><p style="font-size: medium;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="85798" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(172, 29, 16)" data-custom="rgb(172, 29, 16)"><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;" class="layout"><section style="padding: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;" class="layout" data-width="100%"><section style="padd